    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In clique network, the signer notion is basically equivalent to a miner in PoW. And in Geth the first account in your local keystore will be used as the signer unless you specify it explicitly via `--miner.etherbase`.\r\n\r\nAnd as you said, you want to modify the source code a bit for other purposes, you can check the block generation logic here https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/4b309c70065e68321f6ba518f35b0454a5c929a9/miner/worker.go#L977 If you modify the coinbase field then all transaction fee will be gathered to this address.\r\n\r\n**Note, there is no block reward in clique network, only transaction fee**\r\n\r\nAnd I will close this ticket since it's not that relevant with go-ethereum itself.",
